  "message": "feat: Add version_gt and detect_os bash unit tests\n\nExpands bats test suite from 20 to 29 tests:\n- version_gt: 7 tests for semantic version comparison\n- detect_os: 2 tests for OS detection function\n\nAll 29 bats tests pass.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
